 (50, 1, '2012-06-29 22:03:19', '2012-06-29 22:03:19', '<center><img src="http://churchope.themoholics.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/language_2.jpg" alt="" title="language" class=" size-full wp-image-397 " />\n<center><h3>YOU CAN EASILY TRANSLATE IT<br/> TO ANY LANGUAGE</h3>\nThis theme is ready to be translated in other languages than English. It include a .POT file,<br/> from which can be easily created .po/.mo files in the language you need.</center>\n\n<br/>\n<center><img src="http://churchope.themoholics.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/wpml.jpg" alt="" title="wpml" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-598" />\n<h3>MAKE IT MULTILINGUAL WITH WPML</h3>\n\nWPLM makes it easy to run a multilingual website with a single WordPress install. Choose languages for your site and start translating content. You can arrange different language contents in the same domain (in language directories), in sub-domains or in completely different domains.\n\n<a href="http://wpml.org/">Learn more about WPML</a></center>\n<br/>', 'Translation ready', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'translation-ready', '', '', '2012-06-29 22:03:19', '2012-06-29 22:03:19', '', 20, 'http://churchope.themoholics.com/?page_id=50', 0, 'page', '', 0),
