 (561, 1, '2012-07-07 12:27:04', '2012-07-07 12:27:04', '&nbsp;\n<h4 style="text-align: center">Besides the fact that you can change colors, fonts, patterns &amp; there are a lot of custom widgets and shortcodes, you can also set<br/>\n<strong>custom slideshow &amp; layout with any sidebar instance\nfor any page, post or taxonomies!</strong></h4>\n\n\n<br/><br/>\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>1. CATEGORIES</strong></h3>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h5>You can control layout for categories using categories settings same as for post &amp; pages. Here is some examples of what you can do:</h5>\n[button type="simple_button_link" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/category/principles/" target="" ]Full width category[/button] [button type="simple_button_link" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/category/stories/" target="" ]Category with right sidebar &amp; custom slideshow[/button][button type="simple_button_link" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/category/church/" target="" ]Category with right sidebar[/button]\n[button type="simple_button_link" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/category/events/" target="" ]Full width category with slideshow[/button] [button type="simple_button_link" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/category/bible/" target="" ]Category with left sidebar[/button][clear]\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1291" title="categories" src="http://churchope.themoholics.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/categories.jpg" alt="" />\n\n\n\n<br/><br/><br/>\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>2. POSTS &amp; PAGES</strong></h3>\n<hr />\n<h5>You have full control over post &amp; pages layout. Here is some examples of what you can do:</h5>\n[button type="simple_button_link" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/full-width/" target="" ]Full width page[/button] [button type="simple_button_link" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/news/" target="" ]Page with right sidebar[/button] [button type="simple_button_link" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/left-sidebar/" target="" ]Page with left sidebar[/button]\n[button type="simple_button_black" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/post-with-custom-slideshow-full-width-layout/" target="" ]Full width post with slideshow [/button] [button type="simple_button_black" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/custom-sidebar-left-layout/" target="" ]Post with left sidebar[/button][button type="simple_button_black" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/post-with-right-sidebar-layout/" target="" ]Post with right sidebar[/button][clear]\n\n\n<br/><br/><br/>\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>3. GALLERY CATEGORIES &amp; POSTS</strong></h3>\n<hr />\n<h5>You can control layout for gallery categories &amp; posts using categories &amp; post settings. Here is some examples of what you can do:</h5>\n[button type="simple_button_link" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/th_gallery_cat/nature/" target="" ]Full width gallery category[/button] [button type="simple_button_link" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/th_gallery_cat/other/" target="" ]Gallery category with right sidebar &amp; custom slideshow[/button]\n [button type="simple_button_black" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/big-layout-sortable-left-sidebar/" target="" ]Gallery page with left sidebar[/button][button type="simple_button_black" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/th_gallery/portfolio-post-with-slideshow/" target="" ]Gallery post with slideshow[/button] [button type="simple_button_black" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/th_gallery/video-post-with-right-sidebar/" target="" ]Gallery post with right sidebar[/button][clear]\n\n\n\n<br/><br/><br/>\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>4. EVENTS</strong></h3>\n<hr />\n<h5>Events made as custom post with custom settings. That allow you to control layout for events categories &amp; posts. Here is some examples of what you can do:</h5>\n[button type="simple_button_link" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/th_event/summe-meeting/" target="" ]Events post with top &amp; right sidebars[/button] [button type="simple_button_black" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/th_event_cat/2012/7/20/" target="" ]Events list for specific day[/button]\n\n<br/><br/><br/>\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>5. TESTIMONIALS</strong></h3>\n<hr />\n<h5>Testimonials also made as custom post with custom settings. That allow you to control layout for testimonials categories &amp; posts. Here is some examples of what you can do:</h5>\n[button type="simple_button_link" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/th_testimonial_cat/testimonials/" target="" ]Testimonials category with right sidebar[/button] [button type="simple_button_black" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/th_testimonial/731/" target="" ]Testimonials post with left sidebar[/button] [button type="simple_button_black" url="http://churchope.themoholics.com/th_testimonial/732/" target="" ]Testimonials post with slideshow[/button]', 'Unlimited flexibility', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'unlimited-flexibility', '', '', '2012-07-07 12:27:04', '2012-07-07 12:27:04', '', 20, 'http://churchope.themoholics.com/?page_id=561', 0, 'page', '', 0),
 (565, 1, '2012-07-07 12:28:52', '2012-07-07 12:28:52', '<center><h3><strong>ENHANCED THEME CONTROL</strong></h3>\n<h5>Starting version 3.4 of WordPress, you can customize theme options before activating a new theme using Theme Customizer.</h5>\n<br/>\n<hr/><br/>\n<h5>To use this feature, go to Appearance -> Themes and click <strong>"Customize"</strong> link near your theme.</h5></center>\n\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-643 imgborder" title="customize_01" src="http://churchope.themoholics.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/customize_01.jpg" alt="" />\n\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-642 imgborder" title="customize_settings" src="http://churchope.themoholics.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/customize_settings.jpg" alt="" />', 'Default theme customize support, for WP 3.4', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'default-theme-customize-support-for-wp-3-4', '', '', '2012-07-07 12:28:52', '2012-07-07 12:28:52', '', 20, 'http://churchope.themoholics.com/?page_id=565', 0, 'page', '', 0),
 (567, 1, '2012-07-07 12:32:21', '2012-07-07 12:32:21', '<br/><h2 style="text-align: center">This theme supports SEO by Yoast Plugin.</h2>\n<br/><hr/><br/>\n<h4>What is SEO by Yoast?</h4>\nWordPress SEO is the most complete WordPress SEO plugin that exists today for WordPress.org users. It incorporates everything from a snippet preview and page analysis functionality that helps you optimize your pages content, images titles, meta descriptions and more to XML sitemaps, and loads of optimization options in between.\n<br/><br/>\n<h4>WordPress SEO Plugin feature list</h4> [one_half] <ul><li><a href="http://yoast.com/wordpress/seo/#title-description">Post titles and meta descriptions</a></li><li><a href="http://yoast.com/wordpress/seo/#robots-meta">Robots Meta configuration</a></li><li><a href="http://yoast.com/wordpress/seo/#canonical">Canonical</a></li><li><a href="http://yoast.com/wordpress/seo/#breadcrumbs">Breadcrumbs</a></li><li><a href="http://yoast.com/wordpress/seo/#permalink-redirect">Permalink clean up</a></li></ul> [/one_half] \n [one_half last=last]<ul> <li><a href="http://yoast.com/wordpress/seo/#xml-sitemap">XML Sitemaps</a></li><li><a href="http://yoast.com/wordpress/seo/#rss">RSS enhancements</a></li><li><a href="http://yoast.com/wordpress/seo/#files">Edit your robots.txt and .htaccess</a></li><li><a href="http://yoast.com/wordpress/seo/#head-section">Clean up head section</a></li><li><a href="http://yoast.com/wordpress/seo/#api-docs">API Docs</a></li></ul> [/one_half] [clear]\n<br/>\n<h4>Post titles and meta descriptions</h4>\nWordPress SEO let\'s you set templates for titles and meta descriptions for all types of pages, so you could come up with a template and not have to think about it, or you could use the WordPress SEO meta box to completely optimize your post title and meta description, using the snippet preview functionality to see what it would look like in Google. Add to that the chance to enter a focus keyword, which is used to show you how it would bold in your search results, and you have the chance to control everything you want about your listing in Google ...\n<br/><hr/><br/>\n<h4 style="text-align: center">You can learn more about this plugin on official website</h4>\n<center>[button type="churchope_button" url="http://yoast.com/wordpress/seo/" target="on" ]Learn more about SEO by Yoast Plugin[/button] </center><hr/>', 'SEO by Yoast', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'seo-by-yoast', '', '', '2012-07-07 12:32:21', '2012-07-07 12:32:21', '', 20, 'http://churchope.themoholics.com/?page_id=567', 0, 'page', '', 0),
