 (735, 1, '2012-07-09 11:17:55', '2012-07-09 11:17:55', '<br/><h2 style="text-align:center"><strong>HERE IS WHAT OUR CUSTOMERS SAY</strong></h2>\n\n<br/><br/>\n\n<blockquote><h4>ShShares</h4>\nThanks SO much for your help and AMAZING follow through. You all are AWESOME!!! Our site gets so much positive feedback regularly and we just launched it! The viewers thank me, but I thank YOU!!!!\n<br/><img src="http://churchope.themoholics.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/stars.png" alt="stars" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-3488 imgborder" />\n</blockquote>\n\n\n<br/><br/><br/>\n\n<blockquote><h4>ericgmbh</h4>\nHey guys, I would like to show you my result with customizing the theme – http://bigsyphe.com/, I’m quite happy with it! The theme is super-neat.\n<br/><img src="http://churchope.themoholics.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/stars.png" alt="stars" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-3488 imgborder" />\n</blockquote>\n\n\n\n<br/><br/><br/>\n\n\n<blockquote><h4>SouthviewCC</h4>\nAwesome theme, just in case people were looking into it and wanted to see another working example you can find our site here: http://www.Southview.org Highly recommend it!\n<br/><img src="http://churchope.themoholics.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/stars.png" alt="stars" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-3488 imgborder" />\n</blockquote>\n\n\n<br/><br/><br/>\n\n\n\n<blockquote><h4>brandfox</h4>\nLove this theme. Highly recommended : )\n<br/><img src="http://churchope.themoholics.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/stars.png" alt="stars" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-3488 imgborder" />\n</blockquote>\n\n\n<br/><br/><br/>\n\n\n<blockquote><h4>Airielle</h4>\nThese logo has been incredible. I am not as great as I want to be with building sites, but this theme can do anything. And the support is OUT OF THIS EARTH! I have asked these guys 100 questions it seems and no matter what, they get back within a couple hours and even help fix it for me. I feel blessed to have found this. I couldn’t be more 